<sec id="id-8eee1e45-683b-4363-a90f-d2f6582e18ee"><title><bold><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="14584e03-ea24-4afa-91ac-5b072a8468a3" timestamp="1667321959718"?>Installation of breastfeeding rooms in an organization<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="14584e03-ea24-4afa-91ac-5b072a8468a3"?></bold></title><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="3af72a29-6405-48a8-e714-55716556c196" text="[Former Box 8]" timestamp="1675426743689"?><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="a385a976-0978-479f-b5e0-ab3ff272602c" timestamp="1667321951030"?>A company offers a support programme for breastfeeding<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a385a976-0978-479f-b5e0-ab3ff272602c"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="4234a7e8-e194-438e-cae1-fe4e7d2dbeec" timestamp="1670320360815"?>/expressing<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="4234a7e8-e194-438e-cae1-fe4e7d2dbeec"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="8ecfad9c-071a-4de2-de00-7c9f0a551258" timestamp="1667321951030"?> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="8ecfad9c-071a-4de2-de00-7c9f0a551258"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="2f3fc89a-515f-4574-d00d-1df6b556a9de" text="for women and/or lactating persons " timestamp="1670320368642"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="6970a915-25b3-4180-c7cc-b8e1aa2998f2" timestamp="1670320495725"?>breast milk <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="6970a915-25b3-4180-c7cc-b8e1aa2998f2"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="799b567c-97de-4df9-c5f4-19caba9f46b5" timestamp="1667321951030"?>in the organization when they return to work after maternity leave. This programme involves a number of actions:<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="799b567c-97de-4df9-c5f4-19caba9f46b5"?></p><list list-type="dash"><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="57936a80-a019-4bab-f01a-b195e2fbc29d" timestamp="1667321951030"?><list-item id="id-37a677ce-ebee-42ba-af38-de33279d61ab"><p>the supply of breastfeeding rooms in accordance with the regulations in effect, and advice on which equipment to use<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="57936a80-a019-4bab-f01a-b195e2fbc29d"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="55bdd7f8-a01f-4383-f8f8-cd30c7a177c0" timestamp="1670320108404"?>;<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="55bdd7f8-a01f-4383-f8f8-cd30c7a177c0"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="707c8b0a-4374-44bf-9a3e-aaf543c2973c" timestamp="1667321951030"?></p></list-item><list-item id="id-c42db432-ae3a-405b-f9cf-1e122065824d"><p>additional breaks for breastfeeding;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-05131e38-1ba9-4982-aeac-fa8dae561bfc"><p>an online schedule on the organization’s intranet site to enable breastfeeding employees to book slots in the room;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-ab791831-474b-409f-98e7-3ff39d6fbc2c"><p>training the management teams in the benefits of the programme;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-0e5ff867-46db-4be7-817c-14726da5f844"><p>documentation on breastfeeding for pregnant employees.</p></list-item><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="707c8b0a-4374-44bf-9a3e-aaf543c2973c"?></list><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="a89bc511-16f9-4720-d3e4-5b286330a61b" timestamp="1667321951030"?>Organizations that have implemented this type of programme have observed a drop in absenteeism amongst women returning from maternity leave. Women who are able to benefit from this type of programme have expressed their satisfaction in being able to reconcile their family time and work time.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a89bc511-16f9-4720-d3e4-5b286330a61b"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="d7a8429d-3c25-44aa-b599-98fef0fa6908" timestamp="1670320723663"?>Organisations with external visitors can also provide breastfeeding rooms for them.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="d7a8429d-3c25-44aa-b599-98fef0fa6908"?></p></sec>